   // 성공/실패와 무관하게 항상 다음 프레임 예약\\n  }\"\n}"},{"s":"d7b3fdf4","t":"2026-07-15T22:40:24.264Z","r":"user","x":"〔도구 결과〕\nThe file C:\\Users\\FINDER~1.MAK\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\claude\\C--Users-Finders-Maker-workspace\\5693def2-1c95-4f70-a3c1-20fc3abcca9e\\scratchpad\\neon-breakout.html has been updated successfully. (file state is current in your context — no need to Read it back)"},{"s":"d7b3fdf4","t":"2026-07-15T22:40:35.144Z","r":"assistant","x":"〔사고〕\nI need to verify the code works with a syntax check and deploy it, then test on github.io to see if I can trigger and read the error. Since the loop is now guarded, I might be able to catch the actual root cause, but the issue is that the demo needs to run with requestAnimationFrame to hit the error, and hidden tabs pause rAF so I can't trigger it myself—the user will have to do that and check the console, or I could read the error from window.__loopErr if I had a visible tab.\n\nLet me deploy the guard and ask the user to reproduce the issue and share the console error. The guard itself fixes the freeze immediately, so that's the priority. I'll run the syntax check, deploy, and verify it loads without errors on github.io."},{"s":"d7b3fdf4","t":"2026-07-15T22:40:35.147Z","r":"assistant","x":"오류 가드 적용 완료. 문법 검사 후 배포합니다."},{"s":"d7b3fdf4","t":"2026-07-15T22:40:42.399Z","r":"assistant","x":"〔도구 호출: Bash〕\n{\n \"command\": \"SC=\\\"C:/Users/FINDER~1.MAK/AppData/Local/Temp/claude/C--Users-Finders-Maker-workspace/5693def2-1c95-4f70-a3c1-20fc3abcca9e/scratchpad\\\"\\ncd \\\"$SC\\\"\\nnode -e 'const fs=require(\\\"fs\\\");const h=fs.readFileSync(\\\"neon-breakout.html\\\",\\\"utf8\\\");const m=h.match(/<script(?![^>]*\\\\bsrc=)[^>]*>([\\\\s\\\\S]*?)<\\\\/script>/i);fs.writeFileSync(\\\"__chk.js\\\",m[1]);'\\nnode --check __chk.js && echo \\\"JS SYNTAX OK\\\"\\nrm -f __chk.js\\ngrep -n \\\"catch (e) {\\\" neon-breakout.html | head -3\\ngrep -n \\\"window.__loopErr\\\\|항상 다음 프레임 예약\\\" neon-breakout.html\\ncp neon-breakout.html index.html\\ncp neon-breakout.html \\\"C:/Users/Finders.Maker/workspace/game/neon-breakout/index.html\\\"\\ncd \\\"C:/Users/Finders.Maker/workspace/game/neon-breakout\\\"\\ngit add index.html\\ngit commit -m \\\"$(cat <<'EOF'\\nFix freeze: guard the game loop so one exception can't stop rAF\\n\\nThe loop called stepFixed/step/draw/updateX with no error boundary, so a\\nsingle thrown exception skipped the trailing requestAnimationFrame and froze\\nthe whole game (demo and real). Wrap the loop body in try/catch, always\\nreschedule the frame, restore interpolation coords, drop the time backlog,\\nand record the error to console + window.__loopErr for root-cause diagnosis.\\n\\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.8 <noreply@anthropic.com>\\nEOF\\n)\\\"\\ngit push origin main 2>&1 | tail -3\",\n \"description\": \"Syntax check, confirm guard, copy to repo+preview, commit, push\"\n}"},{"s":"d7b3fdf4","t":"2026-07-15T22:40:50.696Z","r":"user","x":"〔도구 결과〕\nJS SYNTAX OK\n411:    get(key, fallback) { try { const v = localStorage.getItem(key); return v === null ? fallback : v; } catch (e) { return fallback; } },\n412:    set(key, val) { try { localStorage.setItem(key, String(val)); } catch (e) {} },\n413:    remove(key) { try { localStorage.removeItem(key); } catch (e) {} },\n3131:      try { window.__loopErr = '' + (e && e.stack || e); } catch (_) {}\n3134:    requestAnimationFrame(loop);          // 성공/실패와 무관하게 항상 다음 프레임 예약\nwarning: in the working copy of 'index.html', LF will be replaced by CRLF the next time Git touches it\n[main 398f4f4] Fix freeze: guard the game loop so one exception can't stop rAF\n 1 file changed, 26 insertions(+), 18 deletions(-)\nTo https://github.com/ukchangjung-commits/neon-breakout.git\n   7d74bab..398f4f4  main -> main"},{"s":"d7b3fdf4","t":"2026-07-15T22:41:00.063Z","r":"assistant","x":"〔사고〕\nI've pushed the guard fix and now I'm verifying the deployment on github.io before republishing the artifact. I want to check if `window.__loopErr` gets populated after loading, though I'm aware the hidden tab won't run the loop long enough to trigger the error. I'm considering whether I can manually invoke the game's step logic to debug further, but it's not exposed on the window object.\n\nLet me just deploy and verify the guard is in place with no console errors on load, then republish the artifact and ask the user to reproduce the issue and share the console error or `window.__loopErr` value so I can track down the actual root cause."},{"s":"d7b3fdf4","t":"2026-07-15T22:41:00.064Z","r":"assistant","x":"구문 OK, 가드 배선 확인, 푸시(`398f4f4`). 라이브 확인 + 아티팩트/시각:"},{"s":"d7b3fdf4","t":"2026-07-15T22:41:03.790Z","r":"assistant","x":"〔도구 호출: Artifact〕\n{\n \"file_path\": \"C:\\\\Users\\\\FINDER~1.MAK\\\\AppData\\\\Local\\\\Temp\\\\claude\\\\C--Users-Finders-Maker-workspace\\\\5693def2-1c95-4f70-a3c1-20fc3abcca9e\\\\scratchpad\\\\neon-breakout.html\",\n \"url\": \"https://claude.ai/code/artifact/a4f4ca1e-f0cd-4d7d-9731-5a48ce1ff3a2\",\n \"description\": \"네온 벽돌깨기 — 루프 오류 가드로 프리즈 방지(+오류 로깅)\",\n \"favicon\": \"🧱\",\n \"label\": \"loop-freeze-guard\"\n}"},{"s":"d7b3fdf4","t":"2026-07-15T22:41:04.798Z","r":"assistant","x":"〔도구 호출: Bash〕\n{\n \"command\": \"date \\\"+%Y-%m-%d %H:%M\\\"\",\n \"description\": \"Get current time\"\n}"},{"s":"d7b3fdf4","t":"2026-07-15T22:41:05.173Z","r":"assistant","x":"〔도구 호출: mcp__claude-in-chrome__navigate〕\n{\n \"url\": \"https://ukchangjung-commits.github.io/neon-breakout/?v=53\",\n \"tabId\": 1930068999\n}"},{"s":"d7b3fdf4","t":"2026-07-15T22:41:08.869Z","r":"user","x":"〔도구 결과〕\nPublished C:\\Users\\FINDER~1.MAK\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\claude\\C--Users-Finders-Maker-workspace\\5693def2-1c95-4f70-a3c1-20fc3abcca9e\\scratchpad\\neon-breakout.html at https://claude.ai/code/artifact/a4f4ca1e-f0cd-4d7d-9731-5a48ce1ff3a2\n\nTo update: republish the same file path in this conversation (keeps this URL), or pass the URL as `url` from any other conversation — a conversation that didn't publish this artifact otherwise mints a new URL. Artifacts are private unless shared from the page's share menu; with Claude Code on the web, the user can browse theirs at claude.ai/code/artifacts."},{"s":"d7b3fdf4","t":"2026-07-15T22:41:09.694Z","r":"user","x":"〔도구 결과〕\n2026-07-16 07:41"},{"s":"d7b3fdf4","t":"2026-07-15T22:41:14.248Z","r":"user","x":"〔도구 결과〕\nNavigated to https://ukchangjung-commits.github.io/neon-breakout/?v=53\n\n\nTab Context:\n- Executed on tabId: 1930068999\n- Available tabs:\n  • tabId 1930068999: \"ukchangjung-commits.github.io\" (https://ukchangjung-commits.github.io/neon-breakout/?v=53)\n<system-reminder>You used a single tool call this turn. Prefer browser_batch to execute multiple actions in one call — it is significantly faster. Batch your next sequence of clicks, types, navigations, and screenshots together.</system-reminder>"},{"s":"d7b3fdf4","t":"2026-07-15T22:41:23.338Z","r":"assistant","x":"〔사고〕\nLet me verify the guard is deployed and check the console for any errors, including checking if `window.__loopErr` captured anything from the hidden tab. I'm realizing the key issue: when the claude-in-chrome tab loads, it runs the initialization once synchronously and kicks off the loop, then schedules the next frame with requestAnimationFrame — but since the tab is hidden, those animation frames get throttled or paused entirely."},{"s":"d7b3fdf4","t":"2026-07-15T22:41:25.469Z","r":"assistant","x":"〔도구 호출: mcp__claude-in-chrome__javascript_tool〕\n{\n \"action\": \"javascript_exec\",\n \"tabId\": 1930068999,\n \"text\": \"(function(){var r={};try{var x=new XMLHttpRequest();x.open('GET','/neon-breakout/index.html?n='+Date.now(),false);x.send();var s=x.responseText;r.guard=s.indexOf(\\\"항상 다음 프레임 예약\\\")>-1;}catch(e){r.err=String(e);}r.canvas=!!document.querySelector('canvas');r.loopErr=window.__loopErr||null;return JSON.stringify(r);})()\"\n}"},{"s":"d7b3fdf4","t":"2026-07-15T22:41:26.041Z","r":"assistant","x":"〔도구 호출: mcp__claude-in-chrome__read_console_messages〕